<p><img src="/assets/rootex_editor_sponza.png" alt="Rootex Editor Sponza Screenshot" /></p>

<p><strong>Rootex Engine</strong> is an advanced 3D game engine written in C++ made by a small team which I am leading at <a href="https://sdslabs.co/">SDSLabs, IIT Roorkee</a>. Rootex is supporting a work-in-progress game, to be released in 2021. It comes with an editor written also in C++ using <a href="https://github.com/ocornut/imgui">Dear ImGui</a>.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/rootex_editor_gif.gif" alt="Rootex Editor Editor Gif" /></p>

<p>Rootex uses DirectX 11 as its rendering backend and we keep adding</p>

